snippet.title: Extra Coin - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://bit.ly/33sdNKr
Join our Discord Server: https://discord.gg/cinicgames

Extra Coin is a narrative side-scrolling adventure game mixing sports and role-playing, set in a virtual social network, where the entire population has devoted their lives. It's a hard story about revenge, failure, resistance, and hiding behind appearances.

Follow CINIC Games:
